BBC.Rugby.Union.2014.11.22.England.v.Samoa.1080i.h264-NX

BBC 2 HD 23rd Nov 2014
1pm to 2pm Highlights

Gabby Logan presents highlights of England's third match of the autumn international series as Stuart Lancaster's team welcome Samoa to Twickenham. It is the seventh meeting between the sides, with England boasting an unbeaten record. The last time they met was in 2010 - Samoa led after half-time but Martin Johnson's side recovered to earn a 26-13 victory. Match commentary by Andrew Cotter and Andy Robinson, with Lewis Moody in the studio.
